		<title>20Technology in the home</title>
		<content>                                       
  62% of children own digital watches  
                                       
 100% of families have a television    
  74% have two or more sets            
                                       
  52% of families have a video         
                                       
  37% own a home computer              
                                       
   6% possess a music synthesiser      
                                       
Source: Junior children at Kingsley    
        Primary school, 19 July 1985   
                                       
                                       
  The information on this block was    
gathered by the children and staff of  
St Werburgh's Primary School, Kingsley 
and of St Mildred's School, Whiston.   
                                       
                                       </content>
